            "creation_date": 1371210715,
            "body": "<p>Be aware that if you call your AsyncTasks like: <code>as.execute();<\/code>, they are not running in parallel. For that you would need to: <code>as.executeOnExecutor(AsyncTask.THREAD_POOL_EXECUTOR))<\/code><\/p>\n",
            "answer_id": 17107865,
            "question_id": 17107688,
            "last_edit_date": 1371211016
        },
