            "is_accepted": false,
            "last_activity_date": 1371212380,
            "creation_date": 1371212380,
            "body": "<p>Why don't make just one notification with information about all the downloads, like total progress. <\/p>\n\n<p>Clicking the multiple downloads notification shows a new <code>Activity<\/code> showing more detailed information about the individual downloads.<\/p>\n\n<p>I personally think users don't like so many notifications and rater see it merged in to one.<\/p>\n",
